OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FCouncil elections are taking place in
OL,7,Fparts of the North East on Thursday 7
OL,8,FMay 2026.
OL,10,FCandidate nominations have now closed,
OL,11,Fas of 4pm on Thursday 9 April.
OL,13,FWhere are elections happening?
OL,15,F- Newcastle
OL,17,F- Gateshead
OL,19,F- South Tyneside
OL,21,F- Sunderland
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
