OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FNormally only a third of council seats
OL,7,Fin Newcastle, Gateshead, South
OL,8,FTyneside and Sunderland are up for
OL,9,Fgrabs at any one time. But now a
OL,10,Freview of local ward boundaries means
OL,11,Fall councillors will be elected in one
OL,12,Fgo.
OL,14,FThat could bring big changes - with
OL,15,FLabour facing real peril.
OL,17,FThey've been leading all four councils
OL,18,F- but are struggling in opinion polls,
OL,19,Flargely based on their performance in
OL,20,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
