OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FOf course they will be judged on their
OL,7,Flocal record too, for better or worse.
OL,9,FLabour have been running Gateshead and
OL,10,FSunderland since the councils were
OL,11,Fformed in the 1970s, and are defending
OL,12,Fa majority of councillors on both
OL,13,Fauthorities.
OL,15,FThey have recently held minority
OL,16,Fcontrol in Newcastle and South
OL,17,FTyneside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
