OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776172268
OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FThe challenge to them appears to be
OL,7,Fcoming particularly from Reform UK on
OL,8,Fthe right, and the Green Party on the
OL,9,Fleft.
OL,11,FReform won Durham County Council last
OL,12,FMay, and are confident of repeating
OL,13,Fthat success in Sunderland this May.
OL,14,FThey could sweep up Gateshead and
OL,15,FSouth Tyneside too.
OL,17,FThe Green Party have surged in the
OL,18,Fpolls under Zack Polanski's
OL,19,Fleadership. They hope to make gains in
OL,20,FNewcastle, and have built a foothold
OL,21,Fin South Tyneside in recent years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
