CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776172268
OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats are established
OL,7,Fas the second party in Newcastle,
OL,8,FGateshead and Sunderland.
OL,10,FThere's no natural Conservative
OL,11,Fterritory up for election in the North
OL,12,FEast this year, but they will look to
OL,13,Fensure they're not left out in this
OL,14,Fnew era of multi-party politics.
OL,16,FSo too will independent candidates and
OL,17,Flocal groupings - who have had a
OL,18,Fsignificant presence in South Tyneside
OL,19,Fand Newcastle recently.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
