CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1776172268
OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FNewcastle is probably the hardest
OL,7,Fcouncil to predict - it could be run
OL,8,Fby a rainbow coalition after the
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FWith only a third of seats up for
OL,12,Fgrabs this year in North Tyneside,
OL,13,FLabour are certain to maintain a
OL,14,Fmajority of councillors.
OL,16,FThey could lose their majority in
OL,17,FHartlepool.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
