OL,3,CWhich North East councils have
OL,4,Celections in May?
OL,6,FIt's a council that has frequently
OL,7,Fchanged hands in recent years, and the
OL,8,Fonly one in our region that will
OL,9,Fdeclare results overnight. The others
OL,10,Fare due to come through in the daytime
OL,11,Fon Friday 8 May.
OL,13,FThose results could increase the
OL,14,Fpressure on the Prime Minister's
OL,15,Fposition, and will of course decide
OL,16,Fwho runs local services in our region.
OL,18,FWhat you need to know
OL,20,F- The deadline for registering to vote
OL,21,Fis Monday 20 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
